metrics.QueryText:
DEFINE
	VAR __DS0Core = 
		VALUES('Sample - Superstore_Orders'[Region])

	VAR __DS0PrimaryWindowed = 
		TOPN(101, __DS0Core, 'Sample - Superstore_Orders'[Region], 1)

EVALUATE
	__DS0PrimaryWindowed

ORDER BY
	'Sample - Superstore_Orders'[Region]

DEFINE
	VAR __DS0Core = 
		SUMMARIZECOLUMNS(
			'Sample - Superstore_Orders'[Customer Name],
			"Total_Sales", 'Parametrs'[Total Sales]
		)

	VAR __DS0PrimaryWindowed = 
		TOPN(1001, __DS0Core, [Total_Sales], 0, 'Sample - Superstore_Orders'[Customer Name], 1)

EVALUATE
	__DS0PrimaryWindowed

ORDER BY
	[Total_Sales] DESC, 'Sample - Superstore_Orders'[Customer Name]

metrics.visualTitle: Total Sales by Order Date and Segment

metrics.QueryText:
DEFINE
	VAR __ScopedCoreI0 = 
		SUMMARIZECOLUMNS(
			'LocalDateTable_fe1a8f94-59c6-46e2-a227-09a3ed0d6de0'[Год],
			'LocalDateTable_fe1a8f94-59c6-46e2-a227-09a3ed0d6de0'[Квартал],
			'LocalDateTable_fe1a8f94-59c6-46e2-a227-09a3ed0d6de0'[№Квартала],
			'LocalDateTable_fe1a8f94-59c6-46e2-a227-09a3ed0d6de0'[Месяц],
			'LocalDateTable_fe1a8f94-59c6-46e2-a227-09a3ed0d6de0'[№Месяца],
			'Sample - Superstore_Orders'[Segment],
			"Total_Sales", 'Parametrs'[Total Sales]
		)

	VAR __ScopedCoreDM0 = 
		FILTER(
			KEEPFILTERS(
				SUMMARIZECOLUMNS(
					'LocalDateTable_fe1a8f94-59c6-46e2-a227-09a3ed0d6de0'[Год],
					'LocalDateTable_fe1a8f94-59c6-46e2-a227-09a3ed0d6de0'[Квартал],
					'LocalDateTable_fe1a8f94-59c6-46e2-a227-09a3ed0d6de0'[№Квартала],
					'LocalDateTable_fe1a8f94-59c6-46e2-a227-09a3ed0d6de0'[Месяц],
					'LocalDateTable_fe1a8f94-59c6-46e2-a227-09a3ed0d6de0'[№Месяца],
					"MinDate", IGNORE(CALCULATE(MIN('LocalDateTable_fe1a8f94-59c6-46e2-a227-09a3ed0d6de0'[Date])))
				)
			),
			OR(
				OR(
					OR(
						OR(
							NOT(ISBLANK('LocalDateTable_fe1a8f94-59c6-46e2-a227-09a3ed0d6de0'[Год])),
							NOT(ISBLANK('LocalDateTable_fe1a8f94-59c6-46e2-a227-09a3ed0d6de0'[Квартал]))
						),
						NOT(ISBLANK('LocalDateTable_fe1a8f94-59c6-46e2-a227-09a3ed0d6de0'[№Квартала]))
					),
					NOT(ISBLANK('LocalDateTable_fe1a8f94-59c6-46e2-a227-09a3ed0d6de0'[Месяц]))
				),
				NOT(ISBLANK('LocalDateTable_fe1a8f94-59c6-46e2-a227-09a3ed0d6de0'[№Месяца]))
			)
		)

	VAR __DS0Core = 
		NATURALLEFTOUTERJOIN(
			__ScopedCoreI0,
			__ScopedCoreDM0
		)

	VAR __DS0IntersectionCount = CALCULATE(COUNTROWS(__DS0Core))

	VAR __DS0PrimaryDbCount = 
		CALCULATE(
			COUNTROWS(
				SUMMARIZE(
					__DS0Core,
					'LocalDateTable_fe1a8f94-59c6-46e2-a227-09a3ed0d6de0'[Год],
					'LocalDateTable_fe1a8f94-59c6-46e2-a227-09a3ed0d6de0'[Квартал],
					'LocalDateTable_fe1a8f94-59c6-46e2-a227-09a3ed0d6de0'[№Квартала],
					'LocalDateTable_fe1a8f94-59c6-46e2-a227-09a3ed0d6de0'[Месяц],
					'LocalDateTable_fe1a8f94-59c6-46e2-a227-09a3ed0d6de0'[№Месяца]
				)
			)
		)

	VAR __DS0SecondaryDbCount = 
		CALCULATE(COUNTROWS(SUMMARIZE(__DS0Core, 'Sample - Superstore_Orders'[Segment])))

	VAR __DS0BodyBinnedSample = 
		SAMPLEAXISWITHLOCALMINMAX(
			3500,
			__DS0Core,
			[MinDate],
			[Total_Sales],
			350,
			'Sample - Superstore_Orders'[Segment],
			ALPHABETICAL,
			ASC,
			105000,
			60
		)

	VAR __DS0SecondaryBase = 
		SUMMARIZE(__DS0BodyBinnedSample, 'Sample - Superstore_Orders'[Segment])

	VAR __DS0SecondaryCount = CALCULATE(COUNTROWS(__DS0SecondaryBase))

	VAR __DS0BodyLimited = 
		SUBSTITUTEWITHINDEX(
			__DS0BodyBinnedSample,
			"ColumnIndex",
			__DS0SecondaryBase,
			'Sample - Superstore_Orders'[Segment],
			ASC
		)

EVALUATE
	ROW(
		"DS0IntersectionCount", __DS0IntersectionCount,
		"DS0PrimaryDbCount", __DS0PrimaryDbCount,
		"DS0SecondaryDbCount", __DS0SecondaryDbCount,
		"DS0SecondaryCount", __DS0SecondaryCount
	)

EVALUATE
	__DS0SecondaryBase

ORDER BY
	'Sample - Superstore_Orders'[Segment]

EVALUATE
	__DS0BodyLimited

ORDER BY
	'LocalDateTable_fe1a8f94-59c6-46e2-a227-09a3ed0d6de0'[Год],
	'LocalDateTable_fe1a8f94-59c6-46e2-a227-09a3ed0d6de0'[№Квартала],
	'LocalDateTable_fe1a8f94-59c6-46e2-a227-09a3ed0d6de0'[Квартал],
	'LocalDateTable_fe1a8f94-59c6-46e2-a227-09a3ed0d6de0'[№Месяца],
	'LocalDateTable_fe1a8f94-59c6-46e2-a227-09a3ed0d6de0'[Месяц],
	[ColumnIndex]

DEFINE
	VAR __DS0Core = 
		SUMMARIZECOLUMNS('Sample - Superstore_Orders'[State], "Profit_Ratio", 'Parametrs'[Profit Ratio])

	VAR __DS0BodyLimited = 
		TOPN(3502, __DS0Core, [Profit_Ratio], 0, 'Sample - Superstore_Orders'[State], 1)

EVALUATE
	__DS0BodyLimited

ORDER BY
	[Profit_Ratio] DESC, 'Sample - Superstore_Orders'[State]

metrics.visualTitle: Total Sales по Месяц и Category

metrics.QueryText:
DEFINE
	VAR __DS0Core = 
		SUMMARIZECOLUMNS(
			'LocalDateTable_fe1a8f94-59c6-46e2-a227-09a3ed0d6de0'[Месяц],
			'LocalDateTable_fe1a8f94-59c6-46e2-a227-09a3ed0d6de0'[№Месяца],
			'Sample - Superstore_Orders'[Category],
			"Total_Sales", 'Parametrs'[Total Sales]
		)

	VAR __DS0PrimaryWindowed = 
		TOPN(
			201,
			SUMMARIZE(
				__DS0Core,
				'LocalDateTable_fe1a8f94-59c6-46e2-a227-09a3ed0d6de0'[Месяц],
				'LocalDateTable_fe1a8f94-59c6-46e2-a227-09a3ed0d6de0'[№Месяца]
			),
			'LocalDateTable_fe1a8f94-59c6-46e2-a227-09a3ed0d6de0'[№Месяца],
			1,
			'LocalDateTable_fe1a8f94-59c6-46e2-a227-09a3ed0d6de0'[Месяц],
			1
		)

	VAR __DS0SecondaryBase = 
		SUMMARIZE(__DS0Core, 'Sample - Superstore_Orders'[Category])

	VAR __DS0Secondary = 
		TOPN(62, __DS0SecondaryBase, 'Sample - Superstore_Orders'[Category], 1)

	VAR __DS0BodyLimited = 
		NATURALLEFTOUTERJOIN(
			__DS0PrimaryWindowed,
			SUBSTITUTEWITHINDEX(
				__DS0Core,
				"ColumnIndex",
				__DS0Secondary,
				'Sample - Superstore_Orders'[Category],
				ASC
			)
		)

EVALUATE
	__DS0Secondary

ORDER BY
	'Sample - Superstore_Orders'[Category]

EVALUATE
	__DS0BodyLimited

ORDER BY
	'LocalDateTable_fe1a8f94-59c6-46e2-a227-09a3ed0d6de0'[№Месяца],
	'LocalDateTable_fe1a8f94-59c6-46e2-a227-09a3ed0d6de0'[Месяц],
	[ColumnIndex]

metrics.visualTitle: Сумма Quantity по Region и Ship Status

metrics.QueryText:
DEFINE
	VAR __DS0Core = 
		SUMMARIZECOLUMNS(
			'Sample - Superstore_Orders'[Region],
			ROLLUPADDISSUBTOTAL('Sample - Superstore_Orders'[Ship Status], "IsGrandTotalColumnTotal"),
			"SumQuantity", CALCULATE(SUM('Sample - Superstore_Orders'[Quantity]))
		)

	VAR __DS0CoreOnlyOutputTotals = 
		SELECTCOLUMNS(
			KEEPFILTERS(FILTER(KEEPFILTERS(__DS0Core), [IsGrandTotalColumnTotal] = FALSE)),
			"'Sample - Superstore_Orders'[Region]", 'Sample - Superstore_Orders'[Region],
			"'Sample - Superstore_Orders'[Ship Status]", 'Sample - Superstore_Orders'[Ship Status],
			"SumQuantity", [SumQuantity]
		)

	VAR __DS0CoreTableByDM0 = 
		SELECTCOLUMNS(
			KEEPFILTERS(FILTER(KEEPFILTERS(__DS0Core), [IsGrandTotalColumnTotal] = TRUE)),
			"'Sample - Superstore_Orders'[Region]", 'Sample - Superstore_Orders'[Region],
			"SortBy_DM0_0", [SumQuantity]
		)

	VAR __DS0PrimaryWithSortColumns = 
		NATURALLEFTOUTERJOIN(
			SUMMARIZE(__DS0Core, 'Sample - Superstore_Orders'[Region]),
			__DS0CoreTableByDM0
		)

	VAR __DS0PrimaryWindowed = 
		TOPN(
			201,
			__DS0PrimaryWithSortColumns,
			[SortBy_DM0_0],
			0,
			'Sample - Superstore_Orders'[Region],
			1
		)

	VAR __DS0SecondaryBase = 
		SUMMARIZE(__DS0CoreOnlyOutputTotals, 'Sample - Superstore_Orders'[Ship Status])

	VAR __DS0Secondary = 
		TOPN(62, __DS0SecondaryBase, 'Sample - Superstore_Orders'[Ship Status], 1)

	VAR __DS0BodyLimited = 
		NATURALLEFTOUTERJOIN(
			__DS0PrimaryWindowed,
			SUBSTITUTEWITHINDEX(
				__DS0CoreOnlyOutputTotals,
				"ColumnIndex",
				__DS0Secondary,
				'Sample - Superstore_Orders'[Ship Status],
				ASC
			)
		)

EVALUATE
	__DS0Secondary

ORDER BY
	'Sample - Superstore_Orders'[Ship Status]

EVALUATE
	__DS0BodyLimited

ORDER BY
	[SortBy_DM0_0] DESC, 'Sample - Superstore_Orders'[Region], [ColumnIndex]

DEFINE
	VAR __DS0CoreNoInstanceFilters = 
		SUMMARIZECOLUMNS(
			ROLLUPADDISSUBTOTAL(
				'Sample - Superstore_Orders'[Category], "IsGrandTotalRowTotal",
				'Sample - Superstore_Orders'[Product Name], "IsDM1Total"
			),
			"Total_Sales", 'Parametrs'[Total Sales],
			"Total_Profit", 'Parametrs'[Total Profit]
		)

	VAR __DS0CoreWithInstanceFilters = 
		FILTER(
			KEEPFILTERS(__DS0CoreNoInstanceFilters),
			OR(
				OR([IsGrandTotalRowTotal], AND(NOT([IsGrandTotalRowTotal]), [IsDM1Total])),
				AND(
					NOT([IsDM1Total]),
					'Sample - Superstore_Orders'[Category] IN {"Furniture",
						"Office Supplies",
						"Technology"}
				)
			)
		)

	VAR __DS0CoreTableByDM1 = 
		SELECTCOLUMNS(
			KEEPFILTERS(FILTER(KEEPFILTERS(__DS0CoreWithInstanceFilters), [IsDM1Total] = TRUE)),
			"IsGrandTotalRowTotal", [IsGrandTotalRowTotal],
			"'Sample - Superstore_Orders'[Category]", 'Sample - Superstore_Orders'[Category],
			"SortBy_DM1_0", [Total_Sales]
		)

	VAR __DS0PrimaryWithSortColumns = 
		NATURALLEFTOUTERJOIN(
			__DS0CoreWithInstanceFilters,
			__DS0CoreTableByDM1
		)

	VAR __DS0PrimaryWindowed = 
		TOPN(
			502,
			__DS0PrimaryWithSortColumns,
			[IsGrandTotalRowTotal],
			0,
			[SortBy_DM1_0],
			0,
			'Sample - Superstore_Orders'[Category],
			1,
			[IsDM1Total],
			0,
			[Total_Sales],
			0,
			'Sample - Superstore_Orders'[Product Name],
			1
		)

	VAR __DS0CoreNoInstanceFiltersNoTotals = 
		FILTER(
			KEEPFILTERS(__DS0CoreNoInstanceFilters),
			AND([IsGrandTotalRowTotal] = FALSE, [IsDM1Total] = FALSE)
		)

EVALUATE
	GROUPBY(
		__DS0CoreNoInstanceFiltersNoTotals,
		"MinTotal_Sales", MINX(CURRENTGROUP(), [Total_Sales]),
		"MaxTotal_Sales", MAXX(CURRENTGROUP(), [Total_Sales])
	)

EVALUATE
	__DS0PrimaryWindowed

ORDER BY
	[IsGrandTotalRowTotal] DESC,
	[SortBy_DM1_0] DESC,
	'Sample - Superstore_Orders'[Category],
	[IsDM1Total] DESC,
	[Total_Sales] DESC,
	'Sample - Superstore_Orders'[Product Name]
